fern.network

Interface ComplexDependenciesPropensityCalculator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PropensityCalculator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SBMLPropensityCalculator

    public interface ComplexDependenciesPropensityCalculator
extends PropensityCalculator
    In a SBML network, the propensities of reaction are calculated by using the kineticLaw tag, which contains a MathML expression. Since therein arbitrary species can be included, there must be a way to fetch dependencies between the reactions in order to create the DependencyGraph.
    Author:
    Florian Erhard
